content: A photo from a walk on 2025-03-29.

photos.alt: A photo of a small park with some houses visible nearby. Close to the middle, a person is walking to the right, holding a paper bag in one hand, and a clothe bag in another. Further away on the path, there is a little girl on a pink bicycle. Even further there is a playground and another person can be barely seen there. There is a lot of green in the photo: grass and leaves, and the sun is shining brightly, leaving many shadows. The sky is mostly clear, with a single cloud barely visible.
